I love Diners, Drive-Ins & Dives, and Season 3 is no exception. He is in the Southwest several times in this season, and finds some really great food and people there. I always find myself smiling while watching this show and it is entertaining and educational.

This set of videos is perfect. Exactly what I expected. I watch these DVDs when I can't find anything else to watch on television. Probably overpriced but I am enjoying them. Received these DVDs when promised and no know problems.
I love this show, and own Seasons 1,2, and 4, but will not shell out $70.00 for season 3.  I only payed $20 for the other seasons, so why would I pay this much for volume three?
